summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4852 for the improvement of Victoria Avenue, from the south line of Lot 1, Block 66, West Seattle Land & Improvement Co's 3rd Plat, to a point 141 feet, more or less, south of West Holgate Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 55829, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
